"{class}`~flexrag.retriever.WikipediaRetriever` which retrieves "
"information from Wikipedia directly. This retriever is adapted from the "
"`ReACT` project."
msgstr ""
"维基百科检索器 {class}`~flexrag.retriever.WikipediaRetriever` "
"：该检索器直接通过维基百科检索相应的实体，该检索器是从 `ReACT` 项目中获取的灵感。"

#: ../../source/tutorial/preparing_web_retriever.md:18
